  <p>(2) Did giving users access to the â€œrawâ€ chart data empower them to see insights you might not have caught and/or caused them to take any actions based on their own analysis? Or was it more for peace of mind and curiosity?</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>(3) Did users find the direct suggestions for changes to their habits really useful and/or take action on them?</p>
</blockquote>

