  <p>(4) Where do you draw the line for what should and shouldâ€™t be â€œdesignedâ€ in the system? Is personal analysis of even things as simple as small trend-graphs or pie charts something that the average user actually does? Or is it just the passionate 1%?
Blanket, lump response.</p>
